> ricknu-0@student.ltu.se wrote:
>> This patch defines:
>> * a generic boolean-type, named "bool"
>> * aliases to 0 and 1, named "false" and "true"
>>
>> Signed-off-by: Richard Knutsson <ricknu-0@student.ltu.se>
